sph.vaadin.ui.videojs

Class VideojsSourceLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • CustomComponent
      • sph.vaadin.ui.videojs.VideojsController
        • sph.vaadin.ui.videojs.VideojsSourceLoader

  • public class VideojsSourceLoader
extends VideojsController
    A controller for Videojs.setSource(String, String) component.

    VideojsSourceLoader is an UI component where an user can set the source of the Videojs.setSource(String, String) component.
